text: Who's Zoomin' Who? is the 30th studio album by Aretha Franklin and released on 9 July, 1985 through Arista. It went to number 6 in New Zealand, number 8 in Sweden, number 13 in the United States and Canada, number 15 in Australia and Norway, number 21 in Switzerland, number 34 in Finland, number 46 in Germany, number 49 in the United Kingdom and number 50 in the Netherlands. It was released after Whitney Houston's debut album. ==Track listing== Category:1985 albums Category:Synth-pop albums Category:Dance albums Category:R&B; albums
title: Who's Zoomin' Who?
